WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:06.766
Then my father scolded me

2
00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:08.400
He said you were an iron-blooded general

3
00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:11.266
A man who values dignity more than life

4
00:00:11.266 --> 00:00:13.100
Did I just realize I was wrong?

5
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.266
Forget it, the past is gone

6
00:00:16.266 --> 00:00:17.933
But you are the only man I like

7
00:00:17.933 --> 00:00:19.133
No one can replace you

8
00:00:19.133 --> 00:00:21.066
I said I won't eat back grass

9
00:00:21.066 --> 00:00:23.000
Go away, are you stupid?

10
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:24.966
Qin Zhan, I am the princess of the Dragon Kingdom

11
00:00:24.966 --> 00:00:27.766
My beauty and wealth are beyond compare

12
00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:28.900
I don't care

13
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:30.366
You are not with me

14
00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:32.866
Then you can't be with another woman

15
00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:40.166
Mom, they didn't do anything to you, did they?

16
00:00:40.333 --> 00:00:41.600
What are you saying?

17
00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:43.966
They treat me better than you treat me

18
00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:45.466
What will happen to me?

19
00:00:45.466 --> 00:00:48.433
Let's go thanks

20
00:00:54.400 --> 00:00:57.966
Mom, you have a daughter-in-law, why don't you tell Mom?

21
00:00:57.966 --> 00:01:00.133
Mom, how can I have a daughter-in-law?

22
00:01:00.133 --> 00:01:01.666
That girl today?

23
00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:03.300
It's beautiful.

24
00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:05.066
You are so lucky.

25
00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:08.200
Mom, I have nothing to do with him.

26
00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:10.666
Did he say he quarreled with you?

27
00:01:10.666 --> 00:01:13.100
So men should be generous

28
00:01:13.100 --> 00:01:14.933
Mom, I know

29
00:01:14.933 --> 00:01:16.000
Mom told you

30
00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.000
This girl's mother likes you

31
00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.866
But it can't be so late.

32
00:01:19.866 --> 00:01:23.000
If the girl has a heart, please choose a good day and auspicious day.

33
00:01:23.066 --> 00:01:24.300
Mom wants to hold grandson

